---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Private Drive">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="bg-white pt-24">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-24 py-20 border-b border-zinc-100">
      <div class="max-w-2xl fade-up">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-4">Legal Document</p>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-zinc-900 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.85] mb-8">
          Terms &<br/>Conditions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Please read these terms carefully before using Private Drive services. By making a reservation, you agree to be bound by these conditions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-24 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-16">

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">1. Rental Agreement</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>Each rental constitutes a binding agreement between you ("the Renter") and Private Drive ("the Company"). The agreement begins at the time of vehicle pickup and terminates upon the vehicle's return and final inspection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">2. Eligibility</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <ul class="space-y-3 list-none">
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6">The renter must be <strong class="text-zinc-900">25 years of age or older</strong></li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6">A valid driver's license held for a minimum of <strong class="text-zinc-900">2 years</strong> is required</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6">Non-residents must present a valid passport alongside their license</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6">A refundable security deposit of <strong class="text-zinc-900">€100</strong> will be charged at the time of reservation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">3. Vehicle Usage</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <ul class="space-y-3 list-none">
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Geographic Restriction</strong> — Vehicles may only be operated within the French Metropolitan area</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">No Smoking</strong> — Strictly enforced; a cleaning fee of €50 applies for violations</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Fuel Policy</strong> — Vehicles must be returned with the same fuel level as at pickup (Full-to-Full)</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Mileage</strong> — Standard rentals include 20 km/day; additional mileage is charged at €20/km</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Condition</strong> — Vehicles must be returned in clean condition; excessive dirt incurs a detailing fee</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">4. Insurance & Liability</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>Renters must provide proof of full-coverage insurance or purchase our supplemental protection plan. The renter is fully liable for any damage that occurs during the rental period. All incidents, regardless of severity, must be reported immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">5. Cancellations & Returns</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <ul class="space-y-3 list-none">
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Full Refund</strong> — Cancellations made at least 48 hours in advance</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Partial Refund</strong> — Cancellations between 24–48 hours incur a 50% fee</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">No Refund</strong> — Cancellations made less than 24 hours before the rental</li>
              <li class="border-l-2 border-zinc-100 pl-6"><strong class="text-zinc-900">Late Returns</strong> — A 30-minute grace period is provided; hourly late fees apply thereafter</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">6. Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>Private Drive shall not be held liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our vehicles or services, including but not limited to loss of revenue, personal injury beyond the scope of our insurance coverage, or delays caused by third-party circumstances.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-primary mb-8">7. Governing Law</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the French Republic. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate courts of Paris, France.</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mt-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
